comments: Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in Beasley's (MIL) path and does not deliver contact during the pick.
Embiid (PHI) loses control of the ball as he attempts to gather, and after recovering, maintains his pivot foot prior to releasing his shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) sets a back screen on Oubre Jr. (PHI) without giving him room to avoid the contact.
Lopez (MIL) legally contests Embiid's (PHI) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Oubre Jr. (PHI) reaches in and any contact with Lillard's (MIL) arm is marginal and does not affect his SQBR.
Beasley (MIL) briefly grasps Embiid's (PHI) arm during the pick, but immediately releases and does not affect Embiid's FOM.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) lowers his arm in an attempt to block the shot and makes contact with Maxey's arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Maxey (PHI) legally contests Lillard's (MIL) jump shot attempt and avoids making contact to his body.
Lillard (MIL) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) establishes himself in the frontcourt within eight seconds.

Replay review of the shooting foul called on Embiid (PHI) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Embiid jumps from A to B and makes contact to Lillard's (MIL) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in screening position in Beasley's (MIL) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) legally contests Melton's (PHI) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
